General.Name: Annehem Fastigheter AB
General.Description: Annehem Fastigheter AB owns and manages commercial, community, and residential properties. The company's property portfolio consists of 25 investment properties with a lettable area of 195,000 square meters. It operates in Stockholm, Skåne, Gothenburg, Helsinki, and Oslo. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Ängelholm, Sweden.
